525
00:47:06,033 --> 00:47:08,619
Kau ingat...

526
00:47:08,660 --> 00:47:10,704
Erik Lehnsherr?

527
00:47:10,996 --> 00:47:13,123
Peramalku melihatnya di Polandia.

528
00:47:13,165 --> 00:47:15,125
Dia meninggalkan beberapa jasad...

529
