Dia baik-baik saja?

1317
01:55:17,708 --> 01:55:19,960
Energinya habis.

1318
01:55:21,378 --> 01:55:22,379
Keluar.

1319
01:55:23,380 --> 01:55:24,340
Keluar!

1320
01:55:24,381 --> 01:55:26,717
