1348
01:59:07,104 --> 01:59:08,856
Seluruh dunia.

1349
01:59:08,897 --> 01:59:10,774
Kau lemah.

1350
01:59:10,816 --> 01:59:11,859
Sama seperti lainnya.

1351
01:59:13,068 --> 01:59:14,194
Charles!

1352
01:59:14,236 --> 01:59:15,195
Kemarilah!

1353
01:59:15,237 --> 01:59:16,864
Selamatkan teman-temanmu
yang lemah!

1354
01:59:18,240 --> 01:59:20,075
Jiwamu ditukar
untuk nyawa mereka!

1355
01:59:22,119 --> 01:59:23,120
Tidak.

1356
01:59:31,253 --> 01:59:32,296
Dia benar.

1357
01:59:33,422 --> 01:59:35,924
Masih ada bagian dariku
terhubung dengannya.

1358
01:59:36,884 --> 01:59:37,801
