02:00:22,513 --> 02:00:23,514
Kini kau di rumahku!

1366
02:00:33,941 --> 02:00:35,943
Kau butuh rumah yang lebih besar.

1367
02:01:55,356 --> 02:01:57,066
Kau mengkhianatiku?

1368
02:01:57,107 --> 02:01:58,108
Tidak.

1369
02:01:59,026 --> 02:02:00,527
Aku mengkhianati mereka.

1370
02:02:28,806 --> 02:02:30,015
Ayo lompat.

1371
02:02:30,057 --> 02:02:30,891
Apa?

1372
02:02:36,313 --> 02:02:37,314
Lindungi aku.

1373
02:02:39,775 --> 02:02:41,276
Mari kubantu!

1374
02:02:46,448 --> 02:02:47,700
Ayo!

