Hank!

1385
02:04:32,554 --> 02:04:33,347
Hank!

1386
02:04:40,813 --> 02:04:43,941
Sudah berakhir, Charles.
Kau kalah.

1387
02:04:43,982 --> 02:04:45,526
Kau milikku sekarang.

1388
02:04:47,986 --> 02:04:50,656
Kau takkan menang.

