Tidak.

1406
02:08:26,413 --> 02:08:27,664
Aku masih bisa merasakannya.

1407
02:08:51,855 --> 02:08:53,524
Terima kasih, Jean.

1408
02:08:55,609 --> 02:08:56,610
Charles?

1409
02:08:57,611 --> 02:08:59,238
