1410
02:09:02,700 --> 02:09:04,368
Di pantai.

1411
02:09:10,457 --> 02:09:12,126
Di Kuba.

1412
02:09:13,919 --> 02:09:15,295
Bersamamu.

1413
02:09:15,713 --> 02:09:17,214
Pantai apa?

1414
02:09:24,763 --> 02:09:25,597
Charles Xavier.

1415
02:09:52,666 --> 02:09:53,792
Maaf.

1416
02:09:54,752 --> 02:09:57,129
Seharusnya aku tidak
menghapus ingatanmu.

1417
02:10:00,507 --> 02:10:01,633
Tunggu!

1418
02:10:06,638 --> 02:10:07,973
Apa yang kulewatkan?

1419
02:10:10,809 --> 02:10:13,395
Tampaknya hanya
oleh pertolongan Tuhan...

1420
02:10:13,479 --> 02:10:14,772
bencana kehancuran...

1421
02:10:14,813 --> 02:10:17,775
di seluruh dunia telah berhenti.

1422
02:10:17,816 --> 02:10:20,319
Pada wawancara hari ini,
Agen Khusus CIA, Moira MacTaggert...

1423
02:10:20,361 --> 02:10:22,654
